- `src/hooks/useLivekitRoom.js` ‚Äî LiveKit room connection
- `src/hooks/useSignalingSocket.js` ‚Äî Socket.IO connection
- `src/hooks/useUserMedia.js` ‚Äî media capture
- `src/components/RealtimeContext.js` ‚Äî context provider (room + socket + streams)
- `src/components/BroadcastStreamControls/index.js` ‚Äî broadcast publish/unpublish
- `src/components/VideoObject.js` ‚Äî broadcast video/audio playback (has visibilitychange fix)
- `src/components/Lobby/index.js` ‚Äî lobby media + selective subscription
- `src/app/api/livekit/token/route.js` ‚Äî token generation with Supabase auth
- `server/index.js` ‚Äî Socket.IO server (mediasoup removed)
